description: Country Grill is a Bay Area food truck that specializes in rotisserie chicken and meats including pork ribs, turkey thighs as well as flavorful side dishes. Serving mostly locally-sourced meats and vegetables from small farms no further than 100 miles from the Bay Area, this truck prides itself on serving organic, free-range and hormone free products from local farms as frequently as possible. Check out the rotisserie chicken, spare ribs, and more!
name: Country Grill
